      <title>哈尔的移动城堡：一年半前的孤独、矛盾和自我救赎</title>
      <link>http://findtreasureisland.github.io/blog.html/%E5%93%88%E5%B0%94%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E5%9F%8E%E5%A0%A1%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E5%8D%8A%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%A4%E7%8B%AC%E7%9F%9B%E7%9B%BE%E5%92%8C%E8%87%AA%E6%88%91%E6%95%91%E8%B5%8E/</link>
